# Task 2 - Student Grade Calculator

This Java program is designed to calculate the **total marks**, **average percentage**, and assign a **grade** based on the marks entered by the user for multiple subjects.

## âœ… Features

- Takes input for marks (out of 100) for each subject
- Calculates:
  - Total Marks
  - Average Percentage
  - Grade based on percentage
- Displays all results clearly

## ðŸ“Š Grade Criteria

| Percentage Range | Grade |
|------------------|-------|
| 90 - 100         | A+    |
| 80 - 89          | A     |
| 70 - 79          | B     |
| 60 - 69          | C     |
| 50 - 59          | D     |
| Below 50         | F     |

